metadata.name: Space Time Memory - T+0072s
metadata.description:
The photograph shows an Aventador LP780-4 Ultimae, lifting off toward the stars. It is the second in a series of five separate NFTs that depict individual moments within seconds from each other as the car rises above the Earth. 

The image was created by capturing more than 1500 individual parts of the car at the factory in Sant'Agata Bolognese (ITA). The element of the Earth's curvature was made by sending a weather balloon equipped with a camera to the edge of the stratosphere. Fabian Oefner then carefully assembled all of these images into a 600-million-pixel photograph, that shows a hyper realistic moment in time, that never existed. 

Space Time Memory - T+0072s is connected to Space Key No. LNFT0002
